  <name>TrenchBroom</name>
  <summary>Level editor for Quake-engine based games</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      TrenchBroom is a level editor for games using the Quake engine.
      It's easy to use and provides many simple and advanced tools to create complex 
      and interesting levels with ease.
    </p>
    <p>
      TrenchBroom has support for several games including Quake, Quake 2, Hexen 2, Half-Life (experimental), among others.
    </p>
  </description>
